org.javaToAvalla.javaScenario.impl

Class ScenarioManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javaToAvalla.javaScenario.impl.ScenarioManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScenarioManagerIF

    public class ScenarioManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScenarioManagerIF
    The ScenarioManager class implements the ScenarioManagerIF interface. It manages the addition of various terms (header, load, set, step, and check) to the Avalla scenario.
